text: Altenhof may refer to: * Altenhof, Mecklenburg-Vorpommern, a German municipality in the Mecklenburgische Seenplatte district * Altenhof, Schleswig-Holstein, a German municipality in the Rendsburg-Eckernförde district * Altenhof, a German village within the Schorfheide municipality in Brandenburg
